      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "一週間後、君達TRINITYAiLEには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In one week‚ you‚ TRINITYAiLE‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ライブバトルへ出場してもらうことが決まった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "will be participating in a live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 213051.0779166329,
          "startTime": 217.6510779166329
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 7.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ライブバトル、ですか\n対戦相手のグループは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A live battle?\nWhich group will we be facing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.933333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "3elements",
      "translations": {
        "en": "3elements.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "VENUSプログラムでは君達よりも上位のグループだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re a higher-ranked group than you in the VENUS program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7333332604053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 17.733333428700767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、聞いたことあります\n私達と同じ、三人組のグループですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ I’ve heard of them.\nThey’re a three-member group‚ like us‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.20000009536744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 28.600000095367434
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリを目前に格上のグループとバトル……\nうちらの実力向上が目的ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A battle against a higher-ranked group just before the Grand Prix…\nIs this for the purpose of improving our skills?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.600000095367434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ。だが、それだけではない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But that’s not the only reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.520692213500535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.57069216581682
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達が、自分達よりも強いグループを降す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s meaning in the story",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.57069216581682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そのストーリーに意味がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "of you defeating a stronger group.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.69573599199453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 40.63996659132341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "確かそういうの……下剋上、って言うんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think that’s called… an upset‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.63996659132341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "そうやね\n話題性はバッチリやんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right.\nIt’ll definitely generate buzz~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.856905468429126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 50.19023880176246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "グランプリに向けて勢いを付けたい\nそのための機会……ということですね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want to build momentum for the Grand Prix.\nSo this is an opportunity for that…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0235721350958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ああ。だが腐ってもプログラム上位のアイドルだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. But they’re still a high-ranked idol group in the program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.19023880176246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "油断すれば容易く喉元を……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you let your guard down‚ they’ll easily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.824349010611584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 63.49023899249733
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "あり得ません。私達三人が油断するなんて……\nましてや、負けるなんてことは、絶対に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s impossible. For the three of us to let our guard down…\nAnd to lose… Absolutely not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.45690565916397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 70.8902389924973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達は、無敗でなくちゃ意味がないんですから\n相手が格上だろうと……勝ちます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have to be undefeated‚ otherwise it’s meaningless.\nWe’ll win‚ even if they’re higher ranked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.25690565916398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……他の二人はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…What about the other two?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3902389924973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 79.05679225139318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちは、瑠依ちゃんがやる気なんやったら\nついていくだけです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Rui-chan is motivated‚\nI’ll follow her lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.82345891805986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "私もです！\n三人でバッチリ、下剋上してきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too!\nThe three of us will pull off a great upset!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.91679227591625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanpresident-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 88.49316410463126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かった。では引き続き、準備はこちらで進める",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright. Then I’ll continue to make the arrangements here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.49316410463126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "君達はレッスンに戻りたまえ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You three should return to your lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.55658787444598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はいっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.87658790986816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 98.00992124320142
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.00992124320142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブバトル当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the live battle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.44325457653476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "さすが、格上なだけあるなぁ\nまだリハやのに、魅入ってしまったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re definitely a higher-ranked group for a reason~\nI was captivated even though it’s just rehearsal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.20992124320148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 107.37658790986815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "激しいダンスなのに、指先の動きまで揃う実力……\n戦う相手として申し分ないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Their movements are so sharp‚ even their fingertips are synchronized…\nThey’re worthy opponents.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.50992124320145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 115.10992124320146
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、さっきスタッフさんが話してたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ I heard a staff member talking earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.10992124320146,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "お客さんの入りは、3elementsのファンの方が\n少し多いかも、だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like there might be a few more\n3elements fans in the audience.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.23658804338254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 124.84332254172442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとしたアウェー戦……願ってもない展開やな\nこれで格下のうちらが勝ったら、めっちゃ盛り上がるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A slight away game… This is the perfect scenario.\nIf we‚ the underdogs‚ win‚ it’ll be super exciting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.27665587505788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 134.5099892083912
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ……だからこそ、しっかり結果を残しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… That’s why we have to make sure we get results.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5099892083912,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6466.666666666526,
          "startTime": 140.97665587505773
        }
      ]
    },
